            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "Sorry..., the error was mine, I have verified that if it reads the configuration file in .config/nvim, whether it is installed from the command line or from Ubuntu snap-store\r\nWhat the snap package did not read was the \"main.shada\", in the snap package it should go in .local/state/nvim while before it was in .local/share/nvim\r\nSorry and Thanks",
